Show inter-module dependency graph for the entire crate

Usage: crawk deps [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -t, --include-tests  Include modules defined in `#[cfg(test)]` blocks (excluded by default)
  -d, --depth <DEPTH>  Truncate module paths to at most N segments.
  -h, --help           Print help (see more with '--help')

